OL,6,FA man who attacked two children with a
OL,7,Fbreadknife has been given a hospital
OL,8,Forder after being found guilty of
OL,9,Fattempted murder.
OL,11,FGeorge Yates, 42, carried out the
OL,12,Fattack in Beckwithshaw, , in June 2022.
OL,14,FYates cut the throat of one child,
OL,15,Fresulting in life-threatening
OL,16,Finjuries, and attempted to do the same
OL,17,Fto a younger child.
OL,19,FA teenager who ran to help when they
OL,20,Fheard screams has been praised by
OL,21,Fpolice for their bravery.
