OL,6,FThey tackled Yates and managed to
OL,7,Fwrestle the knife from him before he
OL,8,Fcould injure the second child.
OL,10,FTwo decorators working at a house
OL,11,Fnearby also rushed to intervene.
OL,13,FThe court heard one of the witnesses
OL,14,Fput their hoodie around the child's
OL,15,Fneck wound to stem the bleeding.
OL,17,FPolice arrived and found Yates in the
OL,18,Fbathroom of a house nearby.
