OL,6,Fsaid he had attempted to take his own
OL,7,Flife and was taken to hospital for
OL,8,Ftreatment.
OL,10,FYates was convicted of two counts of
OL,11,Fattempted murder following a nine-day
OL,12,Ftrial in April last year but his
OL,13,Fsentencing was adjourned so he could
OL,14,Fbe assessed by psychiatrists.
OL,16,FAt Sheffield Crown Court on Wednesday,
OL,17,F13 March, Yates was given a hospital
OL,18,Forder with restrictions.
