OL,6,FHe was told if he is released, he will
OL,7,Fbe closely monitored by mental health
OL,8,Fprofessionals.
OL,10,FDet Ch Insp Steve Menzies said: "This
OL,11,Fwas an utterly horrific and disturbing
OL,12,Fcrime, made all the worse by the young
OL,13,Fages of the victims involved.
OL,15,F"To be attacked in such a violent
OL,16,Fmanner, without any warning, is
OL,17,Fsickening, and sadly something the
OL,18,Fchildren will never forget."
