OL,6,FHe added: "Whilst they have made
OL,7,Fremarkable physical recoveries, and
OL,8,Fshown immense bravery throughout the
OL,9,Fincident, the police investigation,
OL,10,Fand the trial, the emotional effects
OL,11,Fwill be long-lasting."
OL,13,FThe detective paid tribute to the
OL,14,F"outstanding bravery" of the teenager
OL,15,Fwho intervened and thanked the workmen
OL,16,Fwho called 999 and protected the
OL,17,Fchildren from Yates until police
OL,18,Farrived.
